## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Strategy correctly calculates time-weighted voting power based on historical balances
- [ ] Flash loan attacks are effectively mitigated (voting power not instantly available)
- [ ] Gas costs remain reasonable (< 150k gas for power calculation)
- [ ] Integration with existing voting module is seamless
- [ ] All edge cases are handled properly:
  - [ ] Zero balances throughout period
  - [ ] Cycle boundaries and transitions
  - [ ] Very short periods (1-2 blocks)
  - [ ] Maximum lookback periods
  - [ ] Token transfers mid-period
- [ ] Comprehensive test coverage (>95%)
- [ ] No security vulnerabilities in audit

## Benefits

1. **Enhanced Security**: Protects against flash loan attacks and vote buying
2. **Fair Distribution**: Rewards long-term token holders appropriately
3. **Reduced Manipulation**: Makes it expensive to temporarily influence votes
4. **Community Alignment**: Encourages sustained participation over speculation
5. **Flexible Configuration**: Adjustable lookback and minimum holding periods

